        "description": "The super multiverse MR game of the original anime “KAIJU DECODE” by TSUBURAYA PRODUCTIONS x TOEI ANIMATION is now available!\n\nIn the game, due to The Singularity Point, Kaiju appear from another dimension into the real world. Players control The Guardian \"UKU\" in this arcade-style action game, battling \"The Transcendental Warriors\" to repair the universe, now known as The Transcendental World.\n\n【How to Play】\n・Defeat enemies appearing from each lane at the correct timing to defend your base.\n・Attacking at the right time leads to higher scores.\n\n【Tips】\n・The game becomes more challenging as you progress through stages.\n・Characters from TSUBURAYA PRODUCTIONS and TOEI ANIMATION feature in various stages.\n・Compete for scores with \"The Transcendental Warriors\" from around the world!\n\n【Notes】\n・Set up your play area before starting the game. Make sure the table and walls that form your playfield are ready.\n\nⒸTSUBURAYA PRODUCTIONS, TOEI ANIMATION",
